                <div class="content_box">
                    <strong class="v_tit"><a href="/Cases/CasesDownLoad/1/7938" target="_blank">查看全文</a>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;<a href="/Cases/Search">案例查询</a></strong>

                    <table cellspacing="2" cellpadding="0" style="margin:auto; width:750px;" class="infotable">

                        <tbody>
                            <tr><td colspan="2" height="30px" style="font-weight:bold; font-size:14px; background-color:#CCCCCC; padding-left:10px;">显示案例信息</td></tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例编号：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">CSR-0217</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">被浏览次数：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">1205 次</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例名称：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">共赴美好生活：远大的共益理念实践</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">译名：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">A Better Life Together: The Practice of the Concept of Co-Benefit of BROAD</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例作者：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">郑耀洲，刘莹，何春艳，李杨，德青旺姆，邓彦平，胡宏伟</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">作者单位：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">中南财经政法大学</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">指导者：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;"></td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">译者：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;"></td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例企业名称：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">远大科技集团</td>
                            </tr>
                            
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">行业：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">建筑、建材业与房地产业</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">规模：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">大型</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例涉及的职能领域：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">综合管理部门/总经理办公室</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例语种：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">中文</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例正文页数（页）：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">12 页</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例类型：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">描述型</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">中文关键词：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">远大集团；共益；共益型企业；可持续发展；ESG</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">英文关键词：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">BROAD Group,Co-Benefit,Co-benefit-oriented Enterprises,Sustainable Development,ESG</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">中文摘要：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">本案例描述了远大科技集团从产生共益理念到实践共益理念的全过程。首先，远大科技集团总裁张跃在自身家庭的影响以及对外界不断思考的驱动之下，产生为人类创造美好生活的远大理想，并将这个理想贯彻到企业的日常经营管理中。其次，在公司中明确了企业文化的重要性，并将企业文化具体为制度，以道德规范影响员工。最后，远大不断彰显企业的价值观，参与到可持续发展的建设之中，从客户、员工、周围农户、供应商、公益等方面着手实践共益理念：保护环境，研发环保产品，推行绿色生活；提供员工有形和无形的报酬保障员工幸福，与供应商共同成长，让农户和社会受益，实现了经济效益和社会效益的平衡。本案例旨在通过一个真实完整的案例，向学生还原企业实践共益理念的全过程，加深学生对“共益”的理解，为企业的共益理念实践提供借鉴。</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">英文摘要： </th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;word-break:keep-all">This case describes the whole process of BROAD Technology Group from the concept of Co-Benefit to the practice of Co-Benefit.First of all, Zhang Yue, under the influence of his own family and driven by the constant thinking of the outside world, the president of BROAD Technology Group, has created the lofty ideal of creating a better life for human beings, and has implemented this ideal into the daily operation and management of the enterprise. Secondly, the importance of corporate culture is clearly defined in the company, and the corporate culture is specific as a system to influence employees with moral norms. Finally, BROAD constantly demonstrates the values of the enterprise, participates in the construction of sustainable development, from the aspects of customers, employees, surrounding farmers, suppliers, public welfare, and practice: protect the environment, develop environmental protection products, promote green living; provide tangible and intangible remuneration for employees, grow together with suppliers, benefiting farmers and the society, and realize the balance of economic and social benefits. This case aims to restore the whole process of practicing the concept of enterprise Co-Benefit to students through a real and complete case, deepen students&#39; understanding of Co-Benefit, and provide reference for the practice of the Co-Benefit concept of enterprises.</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">适用对象： </th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">本科生,硕士生,工商管理硕士（MBA）,</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">编写方式：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">采编/一手资料编写</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例年代：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">2023</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">适用课程：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">《商业伦理与社会责任》、《可持续发展》</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例涉及理论知识：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">企业社会责任；共益；ESG</td>
                            </tr>
                            
                            
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例入库时间：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">2023-12</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
